Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:06.63,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,In the State of Qin and the State of Wei's fierce battle, Xin and Lun Hu have faced off once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:06.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）秦国(しんこく)と魏国(ぎこく)との\N激戦の中で 再び対峙(たいじ)した信(しん)と輪虎(りんこ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:12.19,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,Which will be the one to surpass their limits and continue on their path?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:12.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限界を超え 己の道を貫き通すのは\N果たして どちらか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:16.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人の熱き思いが今 火花を散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:16.56,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,These two's heated emotions are now making sparks fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:23.31,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,He can't... get up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）こいつは もう―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:23.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち上がれねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:26.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち上がれるはず… が…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:26.87,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,There's no way he... can...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:41.64,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Lun Hu. You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:41.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎 てめえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:46.14,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,My lord is... waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:45.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）殿が… 待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:52.15,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I cannot... lose here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:51.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな所で負けられない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:01:02.91,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs80\be0.25\c&H000000&\pos(600,120)}Precious Comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:11.42,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:11.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は負けられない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:17.17,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I was sent by the heavens to be Lian Po's sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:17.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は 天の与えし廉頗(れんぱ)の剣(つるぎ)だからね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:19.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:19.68,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,The heavens?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.38,Kingdom-Flashback,Lun,0,0,0,,There is only a handful of military commanders loved by the heavens. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:25.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）天に愛される武将は\Nほんの ひと握り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）運命だった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:28.56,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,It was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:34.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき 死にかけていた僕が\N殿に拾われたのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:34.38,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,My being picked up by my lord when I was on the verge of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:36.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天の計らいだった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:36.82,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,was arranged by heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:40.82,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Picked up? By Lian Po?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:40.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,拾われた？ 廉頗に？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:47.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）\N最初は ごく ありふれた話さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:47.73,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,It started out as a very common story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:51.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦渦に巻き込まれた小さな村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:51.54,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,A small village caught up in a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:57.94,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,All of the villagers died, and while my sister and I just managed to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,村人は皆 死に―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:02:00.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かろうじて生き残った幼い僕と妹も\Nただ 飢え死にの時を待っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:01.63,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Still being small children, all we could do was wait to die of starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:05.64,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I don't know how many days had passed when...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから 何日たったか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:19.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）僕は あの人に会った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:19.26,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I met that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.84,Kingdom-Flashback,Lian,0,0,0,,There are some child survivors {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）小僧が生き残っておる\N水と食べ物を与えてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.09,Kingdom-Flashback,Lian,0,0,0,,Give them some food and water. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:25.74,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:29.11,Kingdom-Flashback,Lun,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you... {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… ありがたく…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:35.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし\Nぼ… 僕の前に どうか妹に…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:35.17,Kingdom-Flashback,Lun,0,0,0,,B-But please, before me, help my sister...{Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）それはムリじゃ\N（輪虎）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:40.71,Kingdom-Flashback,Lian,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we can't. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:50.72,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed to say, I hadn't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:50.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）情けないことに\N僕は気づいていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.18,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,My little sister was already long dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妹が とっくに死んでいたことに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:01.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハッ… 妹の話は関係なかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:01.70,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Though I guess the part about my little sister isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:06.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく 僕は命を救われた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.99,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Anyhow, my life was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.49,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,By the Great General, Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの大将軍 廉頗に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶然だと思うかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:11.85,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Do you think that was a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:16.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果的に\N戦いの才能があった僕と 廉頗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:17.04,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,It resulted in me, the fighting genius, fighting alongside Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:22.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦いの天才が\N戦いの大天才に拾われたことを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:23.01,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,The fighting genius being adopted by the great fighting genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玄峰(げんぽう)さまが よく言っていたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:28.59,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Lord Xuan Feng used to say this quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“天に愛される武将は\Nほんの ひと握り”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:32.52,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,"There is only a handful of military commanders loved by the heavens."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:39.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“そのひとりである廉頗に 天が\N出会わせた剣が この僕だ”ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.59,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,And one of those, Lian Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:40.00,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,has me, the sword that the heavens guided to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 僕は…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.82,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.59,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,That's why I can't die in a place like thi—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:49.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 僕は\Nこんな所で負けるわけに…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:50.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）くだらねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.56,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,From what you've been saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきから聞いてりゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:57.54,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,you're making it all sound like this is all something that's in the hands of the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:57.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃ まるで\N全部 天任せみてえじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうじゃねえだろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.65,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:03.17,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We're all standing and fighting on our own legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:03.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは みんな\Nてめえの足で立って戦ってんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:09.68,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Even you are putting your life on the line to fight as Lian Po's sword, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のお前だって―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:09.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗の剣であるために 命懸けで\N戦いまくってきた結果だろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:18.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど\N出会いが重要だってことは分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:18.03,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Still, I know how important chance encounters are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:21.32,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Like how you met Lian Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:22.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が廉頗に出会ったってんなら\N俺だって―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:26.19,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I met with a man who should've become a general even greater than Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:26.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗以上の大将軍に\Nなるはずだった男に出会い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And I grew up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつと共に育った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:34.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（慶(けい)）尾平(びへい)…\N（尾平）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.05,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wei Ping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:33.95,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.68,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Piao...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:50.03,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,He gave me my dream... and died way too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:50.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に夢をくれた そいつは\Nはやばやと死んじまったが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:55.89,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And in his place... I met another out-of-this-world person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:51.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,代わりに―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は また\Nとんでもねえヤツと出会った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:02.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから掛けがえのねえ戦友たちと\N出会い 別れ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:01.98,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Since then, I met with and said goodbye to lots of comrades in arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:08.53,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,and I even met a person that would become a realistic guideline for my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:08.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 俺の道の\N現実的な指針となる人にも会った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:13.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが偶然じゃねえっていうなら\Nそうかもしんねえが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:13.56,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You could say that those weren't coincidences,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:16.69,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,but I know it wasn't some flighty thing like the heavens or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天とか何とか\N浮ついたことは考えねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:21.50,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I just moved forward, carrying the thoughts of those I encountered!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:21.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は 関わったヤツらの\N思いをしょって 前に進むだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:26.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎！ お前と戦ったことも\Nでっけえ糧にしてな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:26.50,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Lun Hu, fighting you will be great fuel for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハッ… 言うねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.76,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,That's what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:33.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 死ぬのは君だから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.76,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,But you're the one who's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:47.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）信 君の言うとおり―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:47.03,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Xin, what you said is correct. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:51.84,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Meetings are fate, and everything past that depends on you. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:51.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出会いは運命で\Nそこから先は自分しだいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:06:00.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし\N天の起こす奇跡も 必ずあるけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:00.59,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,But there are definitely miracles brought about by the heavens...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:05.92,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,My lord...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:05.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎(おうき)が死に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:14.93,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,With the death of Wang Qi and the appearance of the great force that is Li Mu,  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,李牧(りぼく)という大物が現れ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:19.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国軍にも\N若き力が芽吹こうとしている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:19.67,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,even the State of Qin is trying to sprout some new talent.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:25.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時代は やはり\N次の戦乱の世へ移ろうとしています
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:25.48,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,The era is shifting to the next world of wars. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:34.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとしたら 殿が亡命して\N前線から退いた あのとき
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:34.27,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Perhaps when my lord fled his country and left the front lines... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:38.08,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,my duty was complete.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:38.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の役目は\N終わっていたのかもしれませんね…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:43.61,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Even if that is the case, perhaps my fighting here {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:43.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今ここで戦っているのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.95,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,was arranged by the heavens as well? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これもまた 天の計らいか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:02.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか強かったよ 飛信(ひしん)隊 信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:02.48,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,You were quite strong, Xin of the Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:07.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:10.69,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Xin... you... also... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君も また…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:43.68,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Lun Hu. You were an incredible opponent that made me prepare myself to die many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:43.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は 何度も死を覚悟したくれえ\Nヤバイ相手だったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（慶）やった！ やったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.92,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He did it! He really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.40,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,He beat Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎を倒した！\N廉頗四天王の輪虎を倒した！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.02,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,He beat one of Lian Po's Four Heavenly Kings, Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:55.55,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竜有(りゅうゆう)）しかも これで！\N（田永(でんえい)）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:56.43,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:08:00.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,条件だった将軍の首１つを\N成し遂げたぜ バカ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:08:00.72,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,We've fulfilled our condition of taking the head of a general, goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽(ばんよう)）ンンッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:07.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賁(ほん)さま あれは！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.91,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Lord Ben, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（刺す音）\N（魏兵）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:09.92,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,I hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁(おうほん)）聞こえている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）輪虎さま！\N（輪虎兵）くそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:22.22,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Lord Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:23.21,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）ウワッ！\N（兵士）敵が！ 輪虎兵が！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:24.68,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:25.56,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,The Lun Hu soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.34,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Leave them to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（元郭備(かくび)兵）ヤツらは任せよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:31.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（元郭備兵）元郭備兵として\N堂々と引導を渡してやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:31.19,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,As former Guo Bei soldiers, it's our job to put an end to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:34.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！ さっさと そいつの首をはねろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.95,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Xin! Hurry up and cut off that guy's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.94,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,We're to hold it up and let the whole battlefield know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,掲げて回って\N戦場中に知らしめるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）輪虎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.37,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Lun Hu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕(えん)）信どの…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:46.87,Kingdom-Thought,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:51.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）首を持って回らずとも\N事実は ちゃんと広まる！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:51.21,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Even without the head, the word will still spread!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:55.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊隊長の信が\N敵将 輪虎を討ち取ったと―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:56.57,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Pass along that Xin, the captain of the Feixin Unit has killed the enemy general, Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:58.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,触れて回るんだ！\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）楚水(そすい)副長の具合は？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.09,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,How is Vice Captain Chu Shui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.03,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Somehow, he hasn't suffered any fatal wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（元郭備兵）\Nなんとか致命傷には至っていません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:06.56,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,I think we can save him if we stop the bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:07.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出血さえ止まれば 助かります\N（渕）よし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.57,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昂(こう)）尾平さん…\N（尾平）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.92,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,Mr. Wei Ping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.24,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:22.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とりあえず 俺らのほうは\N全部 うまくいったみてえだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:22.06,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,For now, it looked like everything went well for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:28.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥(きょがい)）あっ…\Nうん？ どうかしたか？ 竜川(りゅうせん)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.50,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Long Chuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.75,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,Something's... kinda weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竜川）ちょっと変なんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:37.76,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,I can't see any sign of people in the area where we left Vice Captain Qiang Lei and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:37.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣(きょうかい)副長たちを残してきた辺り一帯\N人影が全くない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:50.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで終わったと思っているのか？\Nめでたいヤツらめ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:50.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Do you think it's over, you joyous bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:56.67,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Lun Hu placed a separate reserve unit next to this main army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:56.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎将軍は この本軍の横に\N別動の予備隊を置いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:10:02.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らが ここに集中したとき\N手薄になった所に突撃するようにな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:59.55,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,So the moment you gathered here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:03.03,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,he could have them charge on the undermanned areas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なんだと！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.66,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:08.15,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,So if you left comrades there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:11.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに仲間を置いてきたってんなら\N今ごろ１人残らず踏み殺されてるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:11.75,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,you can bet that every last one of them's been trampled to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハッ… 何せ 別動隊は―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:19.52,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That separate unit was made up of 500 men from the army of the head of the Four Heavenly Kings, General Jie Zifang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:21.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの四天王筆頭 介子坊(かいしぼう)将軍の\N私兵500だからな ハハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふ… ふざけたこと\N言ってんじゃねえぞ こら！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.94,Kingdom-Main,Qi,0,0,0,,Q-Quit spouting bullshit, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.24,Kingdom-Main,Qi,0,0,0,,Long Chuan, search carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:29.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜川！ ちゃんと捜せよ\Nマジで見えねえのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:29.71,Kingdom-Main,Qi,0,0,0,,Can you seriously not see them anywhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:33.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… この雨だし ここからじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:33.31,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,I-In this rain, it's pretty hard to see from...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪(はいろう)）あっ… 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:35.31,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:38.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（松左(しょうさ)）お… 俺たちも行くぞ！\N（兵士たち）おう！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:37.30,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,Let's go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:43.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,侵略者どもが… いい気味だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.95,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Serves you invaders right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:50.49,Kingdom-Flashback,Xin,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei, I'll see you later. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.46,Kingdom-Flashback,Qiang,0,0,0,,Right. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）羌瘣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また あとでな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.96,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:01.96,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs60\be0.2\pos(392,122.333)}Qiang Lei
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:08.06,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,This was approximately one hour before Xin struck down Lun Hu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:08.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）それは 信が輪虎を\N討ち取る１時間ほど前のことである
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:13.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後方に残ったのは\N羌瘣と負傷兵 およそ200名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:13.35,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei was left behind with approximately 200 wounded soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.72,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's happening with the captain and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（負傷兵Ａ）\N隊長たちは どうなってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（負傷兵Ｂ）\N輪虎と一騎打ちやってるみたいだが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:18.02,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It looks like he's going one-on-one with Lun Hu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:20.02,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,but it's hard to tell much from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:20.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここからじゃ よく分からん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鬨(とき)の声）\Nハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？ あれは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.77,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,What... is that...? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（負傷兵Ａ）\Nて… 敵の新手か？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A new batch of enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（負傷兵Ｂ）\Nで… でかい！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It-It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:36.50,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Foot soldiers are flying this way like a spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歩兵が棒きれみたいに\N吹き飛んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:37.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）く… 来るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:37.96,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I-Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.82,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What are you doing, reserve unit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:41.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）何やってる 予備隊！\N早く応援に来い！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:42.63,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Come here and back us up, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急げ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:46.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（負傷兵Ｃ）あ… あんなの\N俺たちが行っても止められっこねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:46.29,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,W-We can't stop an enemy like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:49.04,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You idiot, what do you think you're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（負傷兵Ｄ）\Nバカ野郎 何言ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.51,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We're a reserve unit put in place precisely for situations like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:51.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういう事態のための\N予備隊だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（負傷兵Ｃ）で… でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.47,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ！\N（負傷兵Ｃ）お… おう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.10,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,We shouldn't go. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:02.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くべきじゃない…\Nこの戦力と 今の自分では―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:02.27,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,As we are now...  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.05,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,we cannot stop a force like that. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:04.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:07.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く来てくれ 飛信隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.90,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hurry, get moving, Feixin Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,副長！\N（負傷兵）羌瘣副長！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:08.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Vice Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.56,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Vice Captain Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:13.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（負傷兵たち）副長！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:10.41,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Vice Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:14.16,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,Big Sis Xiang... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,象(しょう)姉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:21.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ねば 象姉の敵(かたき)は討てなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:21.29,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,If I die... I'll never be able to avenge Big Sis Xiang. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.56,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,If we go, we'll just be running to our deaths!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行っても\Nただ 死にに行くようなもんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめたほうが…\N（負傷兵Ｅ）ふざけるな 貴様！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.46,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We should just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:26.88,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも飛信隊か！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.57,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You call yourself a member of the Feixin Unit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:31.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隊長たちだって今\N命懸けで戦ってんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.80,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Our captain and the others are out there risking their lives right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.85,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Big Sis Xiang.  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:38.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん 象姉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:43.11,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,Right now... I am a vice captain of the Feixin Unit!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:43.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり今は 私は飛信隊の副長だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:47.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ！\N（負傷兵たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.63,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:52.21,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,Damn. Am I really this much of an idiot? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:51.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ…\N私って こんなバカだったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.35,Kingdom-Flashback,Xiang,0,0,0,,Be careful, Lei. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:59.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（象）気をつけるんだぞ 瘣\Nバカのそばにいると バカが うつる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:59.46,Kingdom-Flashback,Xiang,0,0,0,,If you stick close to idiots, their stupidity will spread to you. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:02.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）フッ… それだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.84,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:07.30,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Vice General Qiang Lei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（負傷兵Ａ）羌瘣副長が―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:09.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,笑ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.03,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,is smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:16.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:34.53,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,They're all... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:35.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）みんな… 死んでる\N（田永）くそ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:37.74,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Shit. Where are Vice Captain Qiang Lei and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣副長たちは どこだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥）隊長！\N（信）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.93,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつ まだ息がある\N俺の什(じゅう)のヤツだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.63,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,This guy is still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.46,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,He's from our Shen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 何があった？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:47.11,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:53.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（太関）す… すいやせん\N敵が強すぎて 俺ら 何も…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemy was... too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.26,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:57.20,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But... Vice Captain Qiang Lei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:57.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに 羌瘣副長は―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:02.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただでさえ苦しそうだったのに\Nたった１人で…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:02.27,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Even though he wasn't in great shape to being with... he fought alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣が？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.00,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:08.28,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. We were really useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:08.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すいやせん…\N俺ら ホントに役立たずで…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:14.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They were too strong... The vice captain... The vice captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:12.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツら あまりに すごくて…\N副長が…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:15.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）ここが今の私にとって―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:18.05,Kingdom-Flashback,Qiang,0,0,0,,This is the only place I can call home now. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,唯一の帰る場所だからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:25.12,Kingdom-Flashback,Qiang,0,0,0,,So when this war is over, I'm leaving here. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから この戦が終わったら―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は ここを出ていく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:29.30,Kingdom-Flashback,Qiang,0,0,0,,I don't know how many months or years it'll take...{Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:29.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か月…\N何年かかるか分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:32.55,Kingdom-Flashback,Qiang,0,0,0,,but I'll make sure I get my revenge. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:32.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっちり敵を討つ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:38.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして それが終わって\Nまた帰ってきたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:38.54,Kingdom-Flashback,Qiang,0,0,0,,And when that's done, if I come back again... {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:39.85,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Bullshit...{Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ざけんな… ざけんなよ 羌瘣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.79,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Quit screwing around, Qiang Lei! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:54.01,Kingdom-Flashback,Qiang,0,0,0,,When that happens, I think I'll really be able to move forward with all of you. {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:46.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）そのときは―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:53.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も ちゃんと\Nお前たちと一緒に前に進めると思う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:15:00.44,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,What are you doing, you fucking idiot?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:15:00.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何やってんだ この大バカ野郎が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:04.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.71,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:14.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この辺 すげえ でけえのばっかり…\Nこれが介子坊の私兵か？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.82,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,Everyone around here is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.53,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,Are these Jie Zinfang's men?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:16.54,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,They're all torn to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:17.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）\N全員 ズタボロだ… 何だ？ こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:17.72,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:21.12,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Th... That was no human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:21.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（介子坊兵）ひ… 人じゃねえ\N（尾平･慶）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:25.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あれは人じゃねえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:25.48,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That... was not a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.67,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Huh? You...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前か…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.50,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:08.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカか お前は！\Nこんなんなるまでムチャしやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.86,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:08.27,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,How could you be so reckless that you'd end up like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:13.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んじまったら\N姉ちゃんの敵討ちもできねえんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:13.03,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You can't avenge your sister if you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:18.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひどいな… 私なりに頑張ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.86,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,What an awful thing to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:18.68,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,After I fought so hard like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっちは… 終わったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:23.42,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Did you... finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:26.66,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah. I took down Lun Hu just like I said I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:28.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ きっちり輪虎を討ち取ったぞ\N（羌瘣）そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:28.54,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信…\N（信）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:33.02,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:39.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離せ… バカが うつる\N（信）うるせえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.37,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.20,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Your stupidity is spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:40.09,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）\N羌瘣副長が無事って 本当か？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.56,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Is Vice Captain Qiang Lei really okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ こっちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.64,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah. They're this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:51.07,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,Did the vice captain really beat all these huge guys on his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:51.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昂）このでかいヤツら\N全部 副長１人で？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.36,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,This is superhuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）人間業じゃねえな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昂）うん？ あっ いた！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:55.93,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:00.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）\N什長たち 集まって何してんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.99,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Shen Chiefs are all gathered together. What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.58,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,No way... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:06.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）バカな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.33,Kingdom-Thought,Yuan,0,0,0,,How can that... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:18.69,Kingdom-Thought,Ping,0,0,0,,Q-Qiang Lei is a woman?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きょ… 羌瘣って―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女だったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？ 信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:21.38,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,What's going on here, Xin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:25.30,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you knew that Qiang Lei was a woman the whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:25.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣が女って…\Nまさか お前 知ってたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）なに黙ってんだ お前！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:27.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:30.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）いつから知ってた？\N（去亥）ちゃんと説明しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.84,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,How long have you known this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.38,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,We want an explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田有(でんゆう)）\Nピーピーうるせえぞ お前ら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:35.00,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Quit squealing, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:39.96,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Just how many lives has Qiang Lei saved up until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:39.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田有）今まで 羌瘣に\Nどれだけ命を救われてきた？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:43.87,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if she's a woman or not at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:43.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今更 女だろうが何だろうが\N関係ねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:46.37,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Think about it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しは察してやれや
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:49.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女の身で\Nあんだけの剣技を身に着けて―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:52.30,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,To learn swordplay like that as a woman, then blend in with men on the battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男に交じって戦場に来てるってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:55.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっぽど でけえ何かを\Nしょってんだろうってな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:55.45,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,she must be carrying quite a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.97,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You've got it backwards, Tian You.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）逆だ 田有\N（兵士たち）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:08.39,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,She's actually really "empty".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:08.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に こいつは空っぽなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:13.28,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,There was this horrible law in the place she grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:13.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつの育った場所には\Nひでえ掟(おきて)があってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:17.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その掟の中で こいつは\N幼なじみの姉ちゃんのために―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:19.75,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And because of those, she was planning on dying for the sake of her older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:20.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬつもりだったらしい\N（尾平）えっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:27.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 結果的に 姉ちゃんは殺され\N自分が生き残っちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:27.78,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But in the end, her big sister ended up being killed, and she was the one left alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:33.12,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ever since then, she's been traveling to avenge her sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:33.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,以来 こいつは\N姉ちゃんの敵討ちの旅をしている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:36.46,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That's everything for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:36.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつにとっては それが全てだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:41.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きる目標は\N敵討ちしかなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:41.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Her only goal in life was to get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:47.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとしたら\Nこいつは 敵討ちが終わったら―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:49.68,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,she was just going to kill herself after she got revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで\N死ぬつもりだったのかもしれねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.00,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:58.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 最近 こいつは\N少しずつ変わろうとしている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:58.19,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,recently, she's been trying to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵討ち以外に…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:02.90,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,She's been thinking about things besides revenge... about what she wants to do after...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:05.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵討ちの先にも 生きる場所が\Nようやく見つかろうとしているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:05.66,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,and about finding a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.20,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And that's the Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが飛信隊だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.71,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna ask you guys to pretend you didn't notice this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今更 気づかなかったフリを\Nしろとは言わねえが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:19.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までどおり\N接してくれねえか？ みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:19.85,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,but could you keep treating her like you always have, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:28.85,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,She's... one of our precious comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:28.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつは\N俺らの大事な仲間なんだからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.07,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,It's all right, Lord Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:32.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫ですよ 信どの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:37.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,田有の言ったとおり\N羌瘣どのは羌瘣どのです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:37.65,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Just as Tian You said, Lord Qiang Lei is Lord Qiang Lei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.11,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,It will be just the same as it has always...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:40.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までどおり変わりなく…\N（尾平）今までどおりじゃダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.86,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,It can't be the same as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.80,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wei Ping...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:43.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）尾平…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:47.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女ってのは\N絶対 この先 いつか敵にもバレる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.49,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,It's definitely eventually gonna leak to the enemy that she's a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:51.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしたら 羌瘣を狙うヤツらも\N出てくるだろうし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:51.40,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,When that happens, there're definitely gonna be people that'll target her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:54.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捕まれば\Nひでえ目に遭わされるに違いねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.50,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,And you can bet that some horrible things'll happen to her if they capture her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうならねえように これからは…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:58.00,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,So to make sure that doesn't happen, from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:01.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣の強さに比べりゃ\N屁(へ)みてえな俺らだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:01.75,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Even though our strength is nothing compared to Qiang Lei's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなで 少しずつ―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:06.92,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Little by little, we've all got to become able to protect Qiang Lei together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:06.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣を守っていってやんなきゃ\Nならねえんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ そういうことだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.76,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Well, he's got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケッ…\N尾平のくせに まともなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:15.27,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Wei Ping actually said something pretty decent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:20.04,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,Hey, you're the one getting rescued by her more often than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…て お前が いちばん\N助けられまくってんだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）あっ…\N（竜有）カッコつけやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:22.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Quit tryin' ta act cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:24.34,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）なっ… うるせえ！\N（笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.99,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Better get stronger, Wei Ping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:28.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強くなれよ 尾平\N（尾平）うるせえっつってんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.16,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,I said shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,良かったな 羌瘣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:39.44,Kingdom-Main,Qin,0,0,0,,You must be glad, Qiang Lei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:46.49,Kingdom-Main,Lu,0,0,0,,Okay, how about us old geezers take care of treating Qiang Lei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魯延(ろえん)）\Nそれじゃ 羌瘣副長の手当ては―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:48.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,老いぼれたちが引き受けようかのぅ\N（信）頼む 魯延じい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:48.11,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Thanks, Old Man Lu Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:51.39,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin, you've gotta get fixed up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）信 お前も手当てしねえと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:52.30,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… いてっ…\N（尾平）立てるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:53.72,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:54.78,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:59.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手当ては 脚の止血だけでいい\Nそれより 馬を持ってきてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:57.09,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Just stop my leg from bleeding, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.37,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Somebody, go bring a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平･慶）えっ？\N（信）渕さん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:03.27,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Mr. Yuan, how is the enemy army looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:04.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵軍の様子は？\N（渕）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:08.66,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. They've lost morale after hearing of Lun Hu's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:08.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎討ち死にの報により\N勢いは失いましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:11.33,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,but they haven't been completely routed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:11.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,総崩れというわけでもありません
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:15.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり 輪虎が生っ粋の\N魏国将軍ではなかったことと―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:14.95,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,I suppose due to the fact that Lun Hu was not purely a State of Wei general
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:19.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,侵略される側の士気は\Nたやすく折れぬということでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:19.52,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,their morale raised from being invaded won't easily be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:23.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,優勢ではあるんだな？\N（渕）今のところ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:22.43,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So they have the advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.84,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,As of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:26.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\N渕さん 悪い　ここ任せていいか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.84,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Yuan, could I leave this place to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.22,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どの まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:31.65,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:36.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後に まだ行く所があるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:37.00,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I still have... one last place to go.
